  "detailed_description": "How long can YOU last against an onslaught of dots?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBring diamonds to the center. Ping!<br />\r\nUse a shield or black hole thing!<br />\r\nDiamond-matching dots will pop,<br />\r\nTouch the rest: they will not stop!<br />\r\nWhen you're done there's art to see-<br />\r\nCompete for hi-scores locally!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIncludes 8 modes for colorblind,<br />\r\nany less would be unkind: <br />\r\nAchromatomaly<br />\r\nAchromatopsia<br />\r\nDeuteranomaly<br />\r\nDeuteranopia<br />\r\nProtanomaly<br />\r\nProtanopia<br />\r\nTritanomaly<br />\r\nTritanopia",
